GOVERNMENT OF INDIA (BHARAT SARKAR)
CABINET SECRETARIAT (MANTRIMANDAL SACHIVALAYA)
New Delhi, the 15h November, 2010
The undersigned is directed to say that with effect from the 15th
November, 2010:
Shri A. Raja relinquished the charge of the office of the Minister of
Communications and Information Technology;
(i)
Shri Kapi! Sibal, Minister of Human Resource Development;
Minister of Science and Technology; and Minister of Earth Sciences
assumed the additional charge of the office of the Minister of
Communications and Information Technology; and
(ii)
(iii)
Shri V. Narayanasamy, Minister of State in the Ministry of Planning
and Minister of State in the Ministry of Parliamentary Affairs
assumed the additional charge of the office of the Minister of State
in the Ministry of Personnel, Public Grievances and Pensions.
(K.L. Sharma)
